==Ancient Greek==

===Pronunciation===
*φωνή / phōnē / fo-nay'
*Probably akin to [[φαίνω]] through the idea of disclosure; a tone (articulate, bestial or artificial); by implication an address (for any purpose), saying or language: 

===Noun===
'''φωνή'''

#[[noise]], [[sound]], [[voice]].

